{
  "id": "655096650c3483001bb7bc80",
  "title": "俳句と川柳の違い",
  "created": 1699780608,
  "updated": 1699782019,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "655096650c3483001bb7bc80",
      "text": "俳句と川柳の違い",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780608,
      "updated": 1699780608
    },
    {
      "id": "65509993e5172d0000d21fd8",
      "text": "どちらも17字の短詩 ([575]) である",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781010,
      "updated": 1699781023
    },
    {
      "id": "65509994e5172d0000d21fd9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781011,
      "updated": 1699781011
    },
    {
      "id": "6550982ae5172d0000d21f04",
      "text": "テーマ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780650,
      "updated": 1699780652
    },
    {
      "id": "6550982de5172d0000d21f06",
      "text": "　[俳句]：自然の動植物や地球、宇宙が中心",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780652,
      "updated": 1699781126
    },
    {
      "id": "65509857e5172d0000d21f08",
      "text": "　 俳句も人間を詠むことがありますが、それは自然との関わりにおいて詠まれています",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780695,
      "updated": 1699780698
    },
    {
      "id": "6550983be5172d0000d21f07",
      "text": "　[川柳]：人間が中心であり、人情、人間の暮らし、人生、人の世の出来事",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780666,
      "updated": 1699781526
    },
    {
      "id": "65509863e5172d0000d21f09",
      "text": "　 川柳は人そのものをあらゆる角度から観察して詠みます",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780706,
      "updated": 1699780706
    },
    {
      "id": "65509935e5172d0000d21f0e",
      "text": "　しかし、最近の俳句は、しきりに人間を詠むようになり、逆に川柳も自然を取り込むケースが少なくありません",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780916,
      "updated": 1699780918
    },
    {
      "id": "65509967e5172d0000d21fc9",
      "text": "　[https://www.fukuoka-u.ac.jp/unv_gide/fkus/senryu2012/about.html 川柳とは？｜第8回全国高校生川柳コンクール｜福岡大学]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780966,
      "updated": 1699781481
    },
    {
      "id": "65509b6ae5172d0000d21ffc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781481,
      "updated": 1699781482
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21faa",
      "text": "[季語]の有無",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fab",
      "text": " 俳句は[季語]が入る",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fac",
      "text": " 川柳には季語が入らない",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fad",
      "text": "  >一、俳句には多く四季の題目を詠ず。四季の題目なきものを雑と言ふ。 ([https://www.aozora.gr.jp/cards/000305/files/57350_60028.html 正岡子規 俳諧大要]、第四)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fae",
      "text": "  >一、雑の句は四季の聯想なきを以て、[* その意味浅薄にして吟誦に堪へざる者多し。](同上、強調[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon])",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699781072
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21faf",
      "text": " 例外もある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb0",
      "text": "  無季の句でも俳句と成りうる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "655099b9e5172d0000d21fdb",
      "text": "   [無季俳句]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781048,
      "updated": 1699781051
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb1",
      "text": "  季語の入る川柳もある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "655099c3e5172d0000d21fdc",
      "text": "  　季語が入らないというより、季語という概念がない・季語が入るかを気にしない？[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781058,
      "updated": 1699781082
    },
    {
      "id": "655099e85e90c00000306e2d",
      "text": "  　そういうことかも[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699781094,
      "updated": 1699781111
    },
    {
      "id": "655099aae5172d0000d21fda",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781034,
      "updated": 1699781035
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb2",
      "text": "[切字]の有無",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509d09e5172d0000d21ffd",
      "text": " > 連歌、俳諧の[発句]で、句末に用いて一句を独立させたり、句中に用いて一句に曲折を与えたりする、[詠嘆]の意をもつ語",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699781896,
      "updated": 1699781981
    },
    {
      "id": "65509d3ee5172d0000d22000",
      "text": "  > 終助詞や活用語の終止形、命令形などが主であるが、今日では詠嘆の意で文法的に切れる場合をすべて称している",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781949,
      "updated": 1699781950
    },
    {
      "id": "65509d10e5172d0000d21ffe",
      "text": "  [https://japanknowledge.com/introduction/keyword.html?i=613 きれ‐じ 【切字】｜日本国語大辞典｜ジャパンナレッジ]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781904,
      "updated": 1699781906
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb3",
      "text": " 切字があることが[発句性]をもたらす",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a3b5e90c00000306e31",
      "text": "  連歌の発句の例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699781177,
      "updated": 1699781182
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb4",
      "text": "　  >雪ながら山もと霞む夕べ[_ かな] ([『水無瀬三吟百韻』]・[宗祇])",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699781180
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a365e90c00000306e30",
      "text": "  [地発句]の例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699781173,
      "updated": 1699781185
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb6",
      "text": "　  >夏草[*_ や]兵どもが夢の跡 ([『おくのほそ道』]・[松尾芭蕉])",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699781174
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb8",
      "text": " 切字がない場合は[平句]であることが多い",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fb9",
      "text": "  連歌・俳諧のように、前の句 (または後の句) との内容の関連がある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a245e90c00000306e2f",
      "text": "  川柳の例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699781155,
      "updated": 1699781159
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fba",
      "text": "　  > 子が出来て川の字形に寝る夫婦 ([『誹風柳多留』]・宝暦八年九月二五日)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699781160
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fbb",
      "text": "   [付句]に「離れこそすれ離れこそすれ」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699781195
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fbc",
      "text": " 例外もある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fbd",
      "text": "  切字のない俳句もあるし、切字のある川柳もある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fbe",
      "text": "  現代においては[切字]が古めかしく聞こえるためか、切字が無くても句中に「[切れ]」がある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699781201
    },
    {
      "id": "6550996a5e90c00000306e2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780968,
      "updated": 1699780968
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fbf",
      "text": "俳句の例",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc0",
      "text": " [https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/3bd8bf8f683719c4d8b57b709f1a3d1703299bb7?page=2 俳句は少し言葉を変えるだけで「完成度」が驚くほど上がる...「添削」でわかる俳句のコツ（現代ビジネス） - Yahoo!ニュース]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509d775e90c000002c369a",
      "text": " 　404",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699782006,
      "updated": 1699782010
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc1",
      "text": " いずれの推敲・添削でも「切れ」が重視されているのが伺える",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc2",
      "text": "  >[_ 「死んで」を「死せり」として強く切った。]さらに、季語を「冬銀河」に変え、空間の広がりを出そうと考えた。(p.2)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc3",
      "text": "  >[_ 中七に「なり」と断定の切字を用いて]、「寒鴉」の堂々とした様子を表現しました。(p.3)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc4",
      "text": "川柳の例",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc5",
      "text": " [https://www.asahi.com/articles/DA3S15398717.html?iref=pc_rensai_long_604_article 朝日川柳 山丘春朗選：朝日新聞デジタル]（2022-08-27）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc6",
      "text": " [https://mainichi.jp/senryu/ 仲畑流万能川柳 | 毎日新聞]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc7",
      "text": " [https://event.dai-ichi-life.co.jp/company/senryu/archive/index.html 歴代1位作品｜サラリーマン川柳｜第一生命保険株式会社]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780962
    },
    {
      "id": "65509958e5172d0000d21fc8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780952,
      "updated": 1699780952
    },
    {
      "id": "6550997fe5172d0000d21fd0",
      "text": "いわゆる「[スローガン]」で作るような五・七・五は川柳に分類されることが多いのであろう[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780991,
      "updated": 1699781142
    },
    {
      "id": "65509801e5172d0000d21f02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780609,
      "updated": 1699780609
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a26e5172d0000d21fdd",
      "text": "[川柳の三要素]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781158,
      "updated": 1699781164
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a2de5172d0000d21fdf",
      "text": " [穿ち]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781164,
      "updated": 1699781192
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a63e5172d0000d21fed",
      "text": "  深く掘って物事の本質を取り出して提示し、読者をハッとさせること",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781218,
      "updated": 1699781220
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a42e5172d0000d21fe6",
      "text": " [おかしみ]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781186,
      "updated": 1699781194
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a6be5172d0000d21ff3",
      "text": "  ユーモア、滑稽味",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781226,
      "updated": 1699781228
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a44e5172d0000d21fe7",
      "text": " [軽み]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781187,
      "updated": 1699781199
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a70e5172d0000d21ff9",
      "text": " \t[軽妙洒脱]、爽快でキレのよいこと",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699781231,
      "updated": 1699782019
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a3fe5172d0000d21fe0",
      "text": " > [古川柳]と呼ばれる、おびただしい数の作品から、[川柳味]の源をなす要素を、後の世になって抽出した結果、この三大要素が絞り出されたものです。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699781183,
      "updated": 1699781247
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a3fe5172d0000d21fe5",
      "text": " > この三つの要素は、現代川柳においても確かに重要な屋台骨ですが、これですべてということではありません。世界の体制や文芸の思潮に応じて、「抒情」「真実み」「詩性」「重み」といった要素も重視されています。",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781183,
      "updated": 1699781244
    },
    {
      "id": "65509a26e5172d0000d21fde",
      "text": "　[https://www.fukuoka-u.ac.jp/unv_gide/fkus/senryu2012/about.html 川柳とは？｜第8回全国高校生川柳コンクール｜福岡大学]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781158,
      "updated": 1699781474
    },
    {
      "id": "65509b65e5172d0000d21ffb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699781476,
      "updated": 1699781476
    },
    {
      "id": "655098865e90c00000306e03",
      "text": "from",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780741,
      "updated": 1699780976
    },
    {
      "id": "655098885e90c00000306e06",
      "text": " [cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]さんのプロジェクト ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780742,
      "updated": 1699780986
    },
    {
      "id": "655098885e90c00000306e29",
      "text": "　　参考",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780742,
      "updated": 1699780996
    },
    {
      "id": "655098885e90c00000306e2a",
      "text": "　　 [『俳句実践講義』(岩波現代文庫)]第1講、p.27~40",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780742,
      "updated": 1699781000
    },
    {
      "id": "655098d9e5172d0000d21f0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780824,
      "updated": 1699780824
    },
    {
      "id": "655098d9e5172d0000d21f0b",
      "text": "[/icons/hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780824,
      "updated": 1699780830
    },
    {
      "id": "655098dae5172d0000d21f0c",
      "text": "テーマ、季語の有無、切字の有無、…を並列したい[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1699780825,
      "updated": 1699780853
    },
    {
      "id": "655099115e90c00000306e2b",
      "text": "　下の方のは[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]のプロジェクトから持ってきたやつなので自由に変えてオーケー[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1699780879,
      "updated": 1699780920
    },
